He can be excluded that the commissioner of the 22nd arrondissement, who has resigned from his post since, who has crushed a pedestrian by causing his death last Tuesday, would have driven in a state of drunkenness or dizzy, said Friday Attila Morvai, spokesman for the public minister of the capital after the relative observation was established.
